I have wrote a readme about my map, you can find it when you have download it.
In the download are also many tipps and tricks about the map (where are the teleporter, where you can find guns, where are illusion walls,...).

features:

- 18 cells (in 1 cell can spawn 2 players)
- many teleporters
- many illusion walls
- 1 air shaft
- a t zone texture
- you have 3 weapon machines 
- a spray contest high wall
- a deagle roulet room
- a place to deagle wide throw
- a footballplace on outside
- a battle ring outside
- a deathroom
- a invisible way
- a funy canon
- a disco
- a explosive room
- ....................
